  <brief_title>A Phase I Trial of Alloreactive Cell Infusion Following Transplantation of Haplotype Cells in Patients With Myeloid Malignancies</brief_title>
  <official_title>A PHASE I TRIAL OF ALLOREACTIVE NK CELLS INFUSION FOLLOWING TRANSPLANTATION OF HAPLOTYPE MISMATCHED, KIR MISMATCHED HIGHLY PURIFIED CD34 CELLS IN PATIENTS WITH ADVANCED OR REFRACTORY MYELOID MALIGNANCIES</official_title>
